<bibRefCitation id="EFF34B01FF9FF942FD91F8A0FCE6F870" author="Cardenas, P. &amp; Rapp, H. T. &amp; Schander, C. &amp; Tendal, O. S." box="[637,882,1904,1931]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" pagination="89 - 106" refId="ref26383" refString="Cardenas, P., Rapp, H. T., Schander, C. &amp; Tendal, O. S. (2010) Molecular taxonomy and phylogeny of Geodiidae (Porifera, Demospongiae, Astrophorida) - combining phylogenetic and Linnaean classification. Zoologica Scripta, 39, 89 - 106. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1463 - 6409.2009.00402. x" type="journal article" year="2010">
Cárdenas 
